      • register

        ResourceResolverRegistry register(ResourceResolver resolver)
        Register a resolver. The resolver is later able to indicate if it supports a particular path. The registration order may be important.
        Parameters:
        resolver - the resolver to register
        Returns:
        this instance for fluent chaining

      • getSupportingResolver

        ResourceResolver getSupportingResolver(ResourcePath path)
        Get a resource resolver that is able to handle a particular path. Returns null when no resource resolver can handle the path.
        Parameters:
        path - the path that will be later resolved
        Returns:
        the matching resolver
